{"tid":571323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「如果其它車長不支持行動，咁以後就唔好講話唔公平！」","createTime":"2018-02-24T13:59:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T10:26:07.000Z","uid":29314,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ee224aeb0094a4cae5925358ed44a9800dbb5b10","tid":571323,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T13:59:23.000Z","msg":"葉蔚琳又指，「月薪車長大聯盟」成立僅兩三天，以whatsapp短訊溝通，現時已有逾千名成員。她說，不知道最終會有多少人參與今晚的工業行動，若今次車長肯站出來，她以後願意「辛苦啲」，與同僚團結合作爭取更好的工作環境；<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果其他車長不支持行動，「哪怕得我一個人（參加），我做咗佢哋唔做，咁以後就唔好講話唔公平」。</span>"},{"pid":"d969ef772d0fe9b5dec3f3688033a858e6506175","tid":571323,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T14:05:29.000Z","msg":"其實，會唔會係，大家都好滿意現行既薪酬呢？"},{"pid":"ef7a041af755c0911cf289a691a3eabbdc5166ee","tid":571323,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T14:38:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339c050e51141840c1fe8b2e3fb820f3a134a0b1","tid":571323,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T23:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6c9d447e00c648bfa6686b35f1259dc1185590f","tid":571323,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d969ef772d0fe9b5dec3f3688033a858e6506175","tid":571323,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T14:05:29.000Z","msg":"其實，會唔會係，大家都好滿意現行既薪酬呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T23:38:11.000Z","msg":"傳就話本來有200幾個司機會搞罷工<br />\n呢班人比公司調走哂/比自己人揸<br />\n<br />\n論內鬼既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339e515d6279518ceae5e7db0db1c6e114cb12a1","tid":571323,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:26:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}